WEBVTT

00:05.664 --> 00:06.790
[SEAGULL SQUAWKING]

00:06.965 --> 00:08.796
DINAH:
We came as soon as we got your message.

00:09.334 --> 00:13.236
- What's the problem?
- There's something you both need to see.

00:13.906 --> 00:15.464
[CONNER GRUNTING]

00:20.946 --> 00:23.813
<i>Almost had me that time, Conner.</i>

00:24.249 --> 00:26.774
<i>You deserve a reward.</i>

00:28.487 --> 00:29.749
[BOTH GASP]

00:31.000 --> 00:37.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:57.282 --> 00:58.647
- Dinah!
- Freeze playback!

00:58.817 --> 01:00.409
That never happened!

01:00.586 --> 01:02.781
You need to keep watching. Play.

01:04.388 --> 01:06.186
[M'GANN LAUGHING]

01:07.159 --> 01:08.751
BATMAN:
Freeze playback.

01:08.927 --> 01:10.690
- Ha, ha, ha.
- Don't you laugh!

01:10.863 --> 01:14.492
She and he and...
Oliver, this is not funny.

01:14.666 --> 01:16.793
No. Ahem. No, of course not.

01:16.969 --> 01:21.099
Please understand,
on Mars, this is a common game.

01:21.273 --> 01:22.831
My people all shape-shift...

01:23.008 --> 01:27.308
...but also read minds
so no one is ever misled.

01:27.479 --> 01:30.778
And I am certain Conner knew
he was with M'gann from the very first.

01:30.949 --> 01:33.179
We're not on Mars, J'onn.

01:33.352 --> 01:38.790
No. But my niece does not understand
things are different on Earth.

01:38.957 --> 01:42.518
Then I'll make her understand.

01:42.694 --> 01:44.855
[APPLAUSE AND UPBEAT MUSIC
PLAYING ON TV]

01:47.800 --> 01:49.700
<i>Oh. Hello, Megan.</i>

01:49.868 --> 01:50.857
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

01:51.036 --> 01:52.025
DINAH:
M'gann.

01:52.437 --> 01:54.405
Just a sec.

01:57.075 --> 01:59.600
Okay. Come in.

01:59.778 --> 02:01.006
[SIGHS]

02:05.350 --> 02:10.377
So you can see that among humans,
that game could be very hurtful.

02:10.556 --> 02:14.356
I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.

02:14.526 --> 02:17.324
I'm not upset anymore.

02:17.496 --> 02:21.523
But please, M'gann,
from now on, just be yourself.

02:21.700 --> 02:23.224
This is my self!

02:24.236 --> 02:25.703
This is who I am.

02:25.871 --> 02:30.865
<i>BATMAN [ON PA]:Robin, Kid Flash, Superboy,
Miss Martian, report for mission briefing.</i>

02:31.510 --> 02:35.606
Rumaan Harjavti is the democratically
elected president of Qurac.

02:35.781 --> 02:40.775
Harjavti has been praised as a fair,
wise leader. A humanitarian.

02:40.953 --> 02:44.719
Sure, any friend of Bruce Wayne's.

02:44.890 --> 02:47.859
But five days ago,
Harjavti allied himself...

02:48.026 --> 02:51.792
...with the dictator of the neighboring
nation of Bialya, Queen Bee.

02:52.831 --> 02:54.765
- Not a fan.
- Few are.

02:54.933 --> 02:58.061
But Harjavti suddenly backs
Queen Bee's baseless claim...

02:58.237 --> 03:01.866
...that Qurac and Bialya
were one nation in ancient times.

03:02.040 --> 03:04.736
And has announced
the countries will reunify...

03:04.910 --> 03:07.310
...in two days at a ceremony in Qurac.

03:07.479 --> 03:11.210
<i>After the ceremony,
I will step down as president...</i>

03:11.383 --> 03:14.910
<i>...so that our rightful monarch,
Queen Bee, may rule.</i>

03:15.087 --> 03:19.080
<i>I laud President Harjavti
for unifying our peoples...</i>

03:19.258 --> 03:24.924
<i>...and I will gladly come to Qurac
to be crowned sole leader of our nation.</i>

03:25.097 --> 03:26.997
And the Quracis are okay with this?

03:27.165 --> 03:28.826
Hardly.

03:29.001 --> 03:31.765
They're well aware of the brutality
of Queen Bee's regime.

03:31.937 --> 03:35.202
But Harjavti has censored the press,
silenced all legitimate protest...

03:35.374 --> 03:39.606
...and invited the Bialyan military
into his country to enforce martial law.

03:39.778 --> 03:41.905
Queen Bee has to be controlling Harjavti.

03:42.080 --> 03:44.275
Doesn't she have the power
to enthrall most men?

03:44.449 --> 03:46.917
And some women. But not long-distance.

03:47.085 --> 03:49.713
And we have confirmation
she hasn't left Bialya.

03:49.888 --> 03:53.119
Something else is at work here.
Find out what.

03:53.292 --> 03:55.226
Robin, you're Team leader.

03:55.394 --> 03:56.918
Promotion. Sweet.

03:57.095 --> 03:58.619
Me? What about Aqualad?

03:58.797 --> 04:01.925
Busy helping Aquaman.
You're the next logical choice.

04:02.100 --> 04:05.297
- Great.
- Dude, you totally left me hanging.

04:10.776 --> 04:12.869
<i>ROBIN:
We're right above the Quraci-Bialyan border.</i>

04:13.045 --> 04:15.775
A border the Bialyans
are in the process of ignoring.

04:29.661 --> 04:32.892
No opposition.
Guess Harjavti really is in bed with Bialya.

04:33.065 --> 04:36.057
Wouldn't expect opposition here.
It's an animal sanctuary.

04:36.234 --> 04:39.294
- The Logan Animal Sanctuary?
- You've heard of it?

04:39.471 --> 04:41.962
Guys, tanks have caused a stampede.

04:43.108 --> 04:44.541
With civilians in harm's way.

04:44.710 --> 04:47.679
- I see them. Woman and a small boy.
- We have to help them.

04:47.846 --> 04:50.280
We're way off mission here.

04:50.949 --> 04:52.541
Deploy. But stealth mode.

04:52.718 --> 04:56.085
If the Bialyans know we hit them,
this becomes an international incident.

05:05.864 --> 05:07.024
[COUGHING]

05:15.273 --> 05:16.331
[GASPS]

05:25.384 --> 05:27.375
Oryx!

05:34.526 --> 05:36.619
ROBIN:
Are you both all right?

05:40.165 --> 05:42.030
Mom, Mom, Mom.

05:42.200 --> 05:45.636
We were just saved by Robin
and Kid Flash.

05:46.071 --> 05:49.700
- Superboy and Miss Martian helped too.
GARFIELD: Oryx.

05:49.941 --> 05:53.399
We diverted the Bialyans around
the sanctuary. You should be safe now.

05:54.012 --> 05:56.981
Yeah, coast is clear, Miss M.
You can de-camo now.

05:59.384 --> 06:00.408
Hi.

06:01.820 --> 06:03.310
You may have made things worse.

06:03.488 --> 06:06.082
Bialyan border crossings
are a way of life here.

06:06.258 --> 06:08.590
Usually they wreck a few fences
and move on.

06:08.760 --> 06:10.660
Engaging them
might have made us a target.

06:10.829 --> 06:13.889
Mom. Uncool.

06:14.066 --> 06:17.160
I'm sorry. I should thank you.

06:17.335 --> 06:19.166
This is my son, Garfield. I'm...

06:19.337 --> 06:22.568
Marie Logan. I can't believe
I'm actually meeting you in person.

06:22.741 --> 06:27.474
I've, uh... I've admired your stance
on animal rights for years.

06:27.646 --> 06:30.513
<i>CONNER:
You've only been on Earth six months.</i>

06:32.451 --> 06:33.475
[SNORTING]

06:35.420 --> 06:38.583
The oryx is sick,
and I think you injured this wildebeest.

06:38.757 --> 06:42.386
- Uh... Sorry?
- I suppose it was unavoidable.

06:42.561 --> 06:44.188
But both need to go to our clinic.

06:44.362 --> 06:47.661
The boys can do that.
You and I can, uh, fix your fences.

06:47.833 --> 06:49.266
- That's not exactly...
- Robin?

06:49.434 --> 06:51.197
Please, Mom?

06:51.703 --> 06:53.568
MARIE & ROBIN: Fine.
- Yes.

06:59.344 --> 07:01.335
[SCREECHING]

07:01.513 --> 07:02.673
Hey! Get it off!

07:04.015 --> 07:06.813
Ha, ha, ha. It's okay. Meet Monkey.

07:06.985 --> 07:09.886
Good name. But I hate monkeys. Grrr.

07:10.055 --> 07:11.317
[SCREECHING]

07:11.656 --> 07:16.184
- Looks like Monkey hates Superboys.
- Dude, be glad he only threw a protein bar.

07:21.800 --> 07:24.132
So pretty weird about Miss Martian
and my mom, huh?

07:24.302 --> 07:27.760
- What do you mean?
GARFIELD: I mean she looks exactly like Marie.

07:27.939 --> 07:29.873
- You know, except greener.
- She does?

07:30.041 --> 07:33.568
<i>Well, duh. Especially back
when Mom was a TV star on Hello, Megan!</i>

07:33.745 --> 07:35.975
<i>Wait, Hello, Megan! is a TV show?</i>

07:36.148 --> 07:38.082
I just thought it was something she said.

07:38.250 --> 07:40.616
Yeah, on the TV show.

07:40.785 --> 07:43.015
Way before we were born.
Only one season.

07:43.188 --> 07:45.588
You can't even find it online.

07:45.757 --> 07:48.419
I know Mom has a tape somewhere.

07:56.768 --> 07:59.635
Well, you're certainly a time-saver.

08:00.305 --> 08:02.773
How was it being Megan?

08:02.941 --> 08:04.966
Being Megan? I don't know.

08:05.143 --> 08:07.611
- I was young. It was fun.
- Remember that time...

08:07.779 --> 08:11.112
...you were supposed to make cookies,
only you thought it'd be faster...

08:11.283 --> 08:14.218
<i>...to make one giant cookie...
- Listen, Hello, Megan! was a job.</i>

08:14.386 --> 08:17.355
The person you saw on TV
isn't who I am.

08:20.559 --> 08:24.017
<i>Hello, Megan! The pilot episode.</i>

08:24.863 --> 08:27.297
KID FLASH:
Whoa, you still have VHS?

08:27.465 --> 08:29.399
- Where's your eight-track?
- Wait.

08:29.968 --> 08:32.698
Aircraft, headed this way.

08:32.871 --> 08:35.032
Gar, stay put.

08:39.211 --> 08:40.644
What is it?

08:47.652 --> 08:50.143
- Where's my son?
ROBIN: I ordered him to stay inside.

08:50.322 --> 08:52.415
He's 8, he doesn't do orders.

08:52.591 --> 08:53.717
GARFIELD:
Mom!

08:54.492 --> 08:57.484
It's okay, I got the animals out!

09:00.498 --> 09:02.557
Garfield!

09:06.838 --> 09:08.237
[GROANING]

09:19.452 --> 09:20.612
[GROANING]

09:24.523 --> 09:26.684
MARIE:
I told you there'd be consequences.

09:26.859 --> 09:29.589
Always. Let's get him inside.

09:44.110 --> 09:46.078
[EKG BEEPING]

09:46.279 --> 09:49.874
He's in shock.
He needs a blood transfusion now.

09:50.049 --> 09:51.516
Is either of you O negative?

09:51.684 --> 09:52.878
- No.
- Sorry.

09:53.052 --> 09:55.020
Neither am I. It's the hardest to match.

09:55.187 --> 09:58.452
- I kept a supply in the clinic.
- I can run him to the nearest hospital.

09:58.624 --> 10:02.321
The nearest hospital with a blood supply
is half an hour away at your top speed.

10:02.495 --> 10:04.929
- Longer by Bio-Ship.
- He doesn't have that much time.

10:05.298 --> 10:06.629
What's Superboy's blood type?

10:06.799 --> 10:10.098
- He's Kryptonian. And Miss Martian...
MISS MARTIAN: Might be able to help.

10:10.503 --> 10:13.939
My shape-shifting occurs
at the cellular level.

10:14.540 --> 10:16.508
I think I can morph my blood
to match his.

10:16.676 --> 10:19.110
Please, try.

10:19.645 --> 10:22.978
I'll need to concentrate. No distractions.

10:23.149 --> 10:25.413
Out. All of you, out.

10:51.777 --> 10:53.301
I'm ready.

10:54.613 --> 10:57.673
And on top of all this,
Harjavti steps down tomorrow...

10:57.850 --> 11:00.148
...subjecting all of Qurac to this danger.

11:00.319 --> 11:03.652
- KF, can you find a news station?
- Sure. Which remote is it?

11:05.791 --> 11:07.019
[CLASS BELL RINGING ON TV]

11:07.193 --> 11:08.558
<i>Hello, Megan</i>

11:08.728 --> 11:14.223
<i>School and boys and parents too
Whole lot of trouble for Miss You-Know-Who</i>

11:14.400 --> 11:16.698
<i>- Who?
- Hello, Megan</i>

11:16.869 --> 11:19.736
<i>- Who?
- Hello, Megan</i>

11:19.905 --> 11:25.468
<i>This cheerleader knows the score
Center of attention and so much more</i>

11:25.644 --> 11:27.737
<i>Hello, Megan</i>

11:28.647 --> 11:29.978
<i>Hello, Megan</i>

11:30.149 --> 11:32.811
<i>A little bit distractable
But never too intractable</i>

11:32.985 --> 11:35.419
<i>She's really quite attractable
Okay, a lot distractable</i>

11:35.588 --> 11:38.182
<i>Eventually, she'll get a clue</i>

11:38.357 --> 11:39.551
<i>Hello, Megan.</i>

11:39.725 --> 11:42.250
<i>It's a girl for me
It's a girl for you</i>

11:42.928 --> 11:44.452
<i>Hello, Megan</i>

11:44.630 --> 11:45.654
[HORN HONKING]

11:45.831 --> 11:47.264
<i>Hello, Megan</i>

11:47.433 --> 11:49.993
<i>It's a girl for me
It's a girl for you</i>

11:50.936 --> 11:53.063
Maybe it's a coincidence.

11:53.539 --> 11:54.563
<i>Hello, Megan</i>

11:54.740 --> 11:55.900
[CRASHING & BANGING]

11:56.075 --> 11:58.441
<i>Hello, Megan</i>

11:59.779 --> 12:01.041
[APPLAUSE ON TV]

12:01.213 --> 12:03.704
<i>MEGAN:
Mom, I'm going to the library to study.</i>

12:03.883 --> 12:08.445
<i>But didn't you invite a certain someone
to study here?</i>

12:08.621 --> 12:09.645
[DOORBELL RINGS]

12:09.822 --> 12:11.449
<i>Oh. Hello, Megan.</i>

12:11.624 --> 12:13.558
[AUDIENCE LAUGHING]

12:16.162 --> 12:17.288
[APPLAUSE]

12:17.663 --> 12:20.530
<i>- Conner.
AUDIENCE: Ooh.</i>

12:21.066 --> 12:22.863
<i>I thought you'd never get here.</i>

12:25.771 --> 12:27.739
Oh, yeah, pure coincidence.

12:27.907 --> 12:31.308
MISS MARTIAN:
It's done. All we can do now is wait.

12:31.744 --> 12:33.143
<i>HARJAVTI:
My fellow Quracis...</i>

12:34.647 --> 12:35.739
Is that Harjavti?

12:35.915 --> 12:38.110
<i>...Queen Bee's rule is a gift to Qurac.</i>

12:38.284 --> 12:40.775
Hey, that guy in back. I know him.

12:42.321 --> 12:45.449
MISS MARTIAN: It's Psimon. The psychic
we fought last time we were in Bialya.

12:45.624 --> 12:49.287
He was working for Queen Bee then.
He must be controlling Harjavti for her now.

12:49.462 --> 12:52.056
I remember the headache
from when he brain-blasted us.

12:52.231 --> 12:54.290
We have to get Harjavti away from him.

12:54.967 --> 12:57.663
I think it worked. Garfield's stable.

12:57.837 --> 13:00.931
Good. Because we have our mission.

13:13.619 --> 13:15.814
ROBIN:
Harjavti's alone.

13:22.661 --> 13:24.959
Where's my daughter? Unh.

13:25.498 --> 13:28.331
- Where's Psimon?
- Forget him. Let's get you out of here.

13:34.306 --> 13:39.801
Well, well, American heroes,
here to assassinate the president.

13:39.979 --> 13:42.675
Such a shame we arrived
too late to stop them.

13:42.848 --> 13:44.611
<i>SUPERBOY:
Those are Apokaliptan weapons.</i>

13:44.783 --> 13:47.343
<i>ROBIN: Which they'll use to kill Harjavti,
we get blamed...</i>

13:47.520 --> 13:50.819
<i>...and Queen Bee gets to rule Qurac.
Form up around the president.</i>

13:51.757 --> 13:53.486
<i>MISS MARTIAN:
I've found Psimon.</i>

13:53.659 --> 13:54.683
<i>ROBIN: Wait.
SUPERBOY: I'll get her.</i>

13:54.860 --> 13:56.885
<i>ROBIN:
No. The mission is Harjavti.</i>

14:04.503 --> 14:06.937
[GRUNTING]

14:10.442 --> 14:14.902
<i>PSIMON: Tsk, tsk. Am I the only one to learn
anything from our previous encounter?</i>

14:15.080 --> 14:19.710
<i>You didn't think that maybe if you could
sense me, I could sense you too?</i>

14:19.885 --> 14:24.049
<i>Or that this time, I'd be ready
to use your greatest fear against you?</i>

14:24.223 --> 14:25.212
Unh!

14:25.791 --> 14:31.889
<i>Psimon says, show me who,
or rather what, you really are.</i>

14:33.566 --> 14:35.363
<i>MISS MARTIAN:
No. No. No!</i>

14:35.534 --> 14:37.968
<i>This is who I am!</i>

14:38.404 --> 14:39.598
[GRUNTING]

14:41.907 --> 14:43.636
[ROARING]

14:47.680 --> 14:49.648
[SOLDIERS GROANING]

14:51.250 --> 14:55.516
Thank you for saving my father.
We will take care of him now.

14:55.822 --> 14:58.484
<i>SUPERBOY:
M'gann, we're coming. Aah! Unh!</i>

14:59.859 --> 15:02.726
<i>PSIMON:
Psimon says smartly done.</i>

15:02.895 --> 15:05.056
<i>Brain-blasting your own team.</i>

15:05.231 --> 15:10.863
<i>I had no idea you'd go to such lengths to
hide your true self from your good friends.</i>

15:11.037 --> 15:12.402
<i>Well, actually, I did.</i>

15:12.572 --> 15:16.804
<i>But you needn't have bothered,
it's being recorded for posterity.</i>

15:17.243 --> 15:18.938
<i>MISS MARTIAN:
No!</i>

15:21.114 --> 15:24.811
<i>PSIMON:
Uh-uh-uh. I didn't say "Psimon says."</i>

15:29.522 --> 15:31.251
[SCREAMS]

15:32.658 --> 15:33.920
Unh!

15:38.798 --> 15:39.822
[GROANS]

15:48.975 --> 15:52.604
<i>PSIMON: Come now, we both know
that's not who you really are.</i>

15:52.778 --> 15:55.770
<i>Must you even lie to yourself
within your own mind?</i>

15:55.948 --> 15:59.076
It's not a lie! This is who I am!

16:02.822 --> 16:05.586
<i>PSIMON:
Wow. And they say I'm pathological.</i>

16:07.527 --> 16:09.188
MISS MARTIAN:
Unh!

16:12.231 --> 16:13.960
Off our game, are we?

16:14.133 --> 16:18.502
Let's dig a little deeper,
find out what we're really afraid of. Hm?

16:18.971 --> 16:20.598
Aah!

16:24.043 --> 16:25.067
[ALL GASP]

16:25.244 --> 16:26.370
Keep back!

16:27.547 --> 16:32.883
<i>PSIMON: Well, of course, friends and teammates
shrink from you in fear.</i>

16:33.052 --> 16:35.612
You should have told us the truth.

16:35.788 --> 16:38.018
I don't see how we can trust you now.

16:38.824 --> 16:41.349
<i>PSIMON:
Then you're kicked off the pep squad.</i>

16:41.527 --> 16:47.659
I am sorry M'gann,
but there is no place for you on Earth now.

16:49.569 --> 16:52.936
<i>PSIMON:
Oh, and banished to Mars too.</i>

16:56.809 --> 16:59.175
<i>Yet even that's not the worst, is it?</i>

17:02.215 --> 17:05.513
<i>MISS MARTIAN:
No, please, stop.</i>

17:08.320 --> 17:11.983
Love you? I can't even look at you.

17:12.157 --> 17:14.022
[MISS MARTIAN SOBBING]

17:15.493 --> 17:19.657
Oh, what you wouldn't do
to prevent that now, right?

17:20.098 --> 17:22.124
<i>MISS MARTIAN:
That's right.</i>

17:25.137 --> 17:28.868
Now, now, my pretty, I know you
don't want to do anything you'll regret.

17:29.041 --> 17:31.566
<i>MISS MARTIAN:
You don't know me at all!</i>

17:36.048 --> 17:37.709
Aah!

17:40.786 --> 17:43.414
SUPERBOY: Unh.
- Conner? You okay?

17:44.190 --> 17:45.555
[GROANING]

17:45.825 --> 17:48.658
Unh! And there's the headache.

17:48.828 --> 17:50.523
Psimon?

17:50.896 --> 17:53.194
He brain-blasted you. I stopped him.

17:59.272 --> 18:00.933
[CAMERAS CLICKING]

18:04.944 --> 18:07.742
What do you mean
the president won't see me?

18:07.913 --> 18:09.380
He invited me.

18:09.548 --> 18:12.608
HARJAVTI:
Not of my free will, no!

18:12.785 --> 18:16.050
But now that I am free
of your minion's thrall...

18:16.222 --> 18:21.285
<i>...the Quraci people will never
suffer your tyrannical rule!</i>

18:21.460 --> 18:23.428
[CROWD CHEERING ON TV]

18:25.097 --> 18:28.999
<i>Mark me, Harjavti, you will suffer for this.</i>

18:29.168 --> 18:31.068
<i>Qurac will be mine.</i>

18:37.576 --> 18:40.841
Sorry you had to lie to everyone.
I couldn't think of any other way...

18:41.013 --> 18:43.413
...to convince the public
Queen Bee was behind this.

18:43.582 --> 18:48.178
Dude, saving a country.
Pretty big win for your first turn as leader.

18:48.354 --> 18:50.618
Yeah, thanks.

18:54.593 --> 18:57.187
<i>And I assure you,
the Wayne Foundation is here...</i>

18:57.363 --> 19:02.164
<i>...to do whatever it can
to help you and your people rebuild Qurac.</i>

19:03.369 --> 19:05.963
Gee, Bruce Wayne sure got here fast.

19:06.138 --> 19:07.605
Almost like he knew... Unh!

19:07.773 --> 19:10.298
Don't you have a souvenir
to collect or something?

19:10.476 --> 19:12.535
Hello, Megan.

19:15.548 --> 19:18.540
Something you'd like to tell us?

19:23.889 --> 19:25.151
[SIGHS]

19:25.324 --> 19:28.691
Growing up on Mars
was not a happy time for me.

19:28.861 --> 19:31.659
I started watching the broadcasts
my uncle sent from Earth...

19:31.831 --> 19:33.662
...to teach us about our sister planet.

19:33.833 --> 19:37.234
<i>And when I saw Hello, Megan!
Something just clicked.</i>

19:37.403 --> 19:39.371
Maybe it was the similarities
in our names.

19:39.538 --> 19:42.996
Maybe it was the way all Megan's problems
could be solved in 22 minutes.

19:43.175 --> 19:46.838
All I know for sure is that Megan helped
me smile through a lonely childhood.

19:47.012 --> 19:53.542
So when I came to Earth and had
to adopt a human form, I chose you.

19:53.719 --> 19:56.483
Well, Megan.

19:57.823 --> 20:02.157
Which begs the question,
what do you really look like?

20:10.569 --> 20:11.900
KID FLASH:
Bald M'gann.

20:12.405 --> 20:14.305
Still hot.

20:18.177 --> 20:20.475
You know you don't have
to put on a mask for me.

20:20.646 --> 20:22.204
I do it for me.

20:22.381 --> 20:25.612
This is who I am inside.

20:25.785 --> 20:27.218
Please don't be mad.

20:28.087 --> 20:30.453
Mad? I'm honored.

20:30.623 --> 20:32.488
M'gann, you saved my son.

20:32.658 --> 20:37.561
He says he's your blood brother now,
and I agree. You're family.

20:40.299 --> 20:44.258
Thank you.
You can't know what that means to me.

20:50.876 --> 20:52.605
Garfield?

20:56.115 --> 20:59.107
Shh. It would be a shame to wake him.

20:59.285 --> 21:04.086
I might have to order my little thrall here
to damage himself.

21:05.624 --> 21:11.654
Uh-uh. He already has orders to do just that
if anything happens to me.

21:13.999 --> 21:18.231
Now, your performance,
a bit over the top, I think.

21:18.404 --> 21:24.172
But then you haven't practiced me
the way you've perfected the role of Megan.

21:25.845 --> 21:27.472
That's right.

21:27.646 --> 21:31.980
Poor Psimon's not the only one
who knows your true form.

21:32.151 --> 21:34.517
And if you don't cooperate...

21:34.687 --> 21:40.455
...I'll make sure everyone knows
what you really are.

